}{\trowd\trleft0\trgaph60
\clvertalt\cellx9430
\pard\intbl\ql
{Upon successful completion of this course, students will be able to 
\line
\_ use advanced functions of office software effectively, \line
\_ analyse data in the spread sheet application Microsoft Excel, \line
\_ prepare well\_arranged text documents in Microsoft Word, \line
\_ prepare impressive presentations in Microsoft PowerPoint, \line
\_ process information in Microsoft OneNote\'2e \line
The students will be able to: \line
\_ prepare individual presentation on IT topic within seminar work, 
\line
\_ defence their own project (both at colloquium and during defence)\'2e 
\line
 \line
\line
}\cell\row\pard
